# 🔍 Complete Issues Report — AURA (Frontend + Backend + CORS + Connection)

All files in both `myapp/src/` (frontend) and `backend/app/` (backend) have been reviewed.

---

## PART 1 — FRONTEND IMPORT ISSUES

### 🚨 Critical (will crash the app)

| # | File | Issue | Fix |
|---|------|-------|-----|
| 1 | `App.jsx` | Inline components (lines 72–187) use `useTheme()` and `cls()` but **neither is imported** | Remove unused inline component definitions (they duplicate files in `components/ui/`) |
| 2 | `WalletPage.jsx` | `wallets` state never declared — `wallets.reduce()` (L28) and `wallets.map()` (L95) will crash | Add `const [wallets, setWallets] = useState([])` |
| 3 | `TokensPage.jsx` | Calls `getUserWallets()` and `setWallets()` — **neither imported nor defined** | Import `getUserWallets` from `../api/api` + declare `wallets`/`setWallets` state |
| 4 | `TokensPage.jsx` | Uses `{w.wallet_type}` (L78) — `w` is **undefined** in that scope | Replace `w.wallet_type` with the correct token property |

### ⚠️ Moderate (unused/duplicate imports)

| # | File | Issue |
|---|------|-------|
| 5 | `App.jsx` | `Outlet`, `useLocation`, `useNavigate` imported but never used |
| 6 | `App.jsx` | 22+ Lucide icons imported for inline components that duplicate separate files |
| 7 | `Badge.jsx` | `useTheme`, `T` imported but never used |
| 8 | `Button.jsx` | `useTheme`, `T` imported but never used |
| 9 | `MiniLineChart.jsx` | `React`, `useTheme`, `T` imported but never used |
