|---|------|-------|
| 4 | `routes/risk.py` L6 | `from app.models.risk import RiskLog` — imported but never used |
| 5 | `services/token_service.py` L9 | `from app.models.risk import RiskLog` — imported but never used |
| 6 | `utils/payment_packet.py` L4 | `from datetime import datetime` — uses deprecated `datetime.utcnow()` instead of `datetime.now(timezone.utc)` |

